divs: Sighting DetailsWe were throwing football and I looked up and saw a disc shaped object. Five minutes later saw two more above the house. It didn't move at all and it seemed like it was higher than a typical jet. We didn't know what to think and we had just seen an advertizement about testing a national alarm on November 9, 2011. It is still in sight but, the other two are gone.
